Instructions:
To run the game, run the main method of the RunGame class in the main package.

Commands (Type these keywords to perform certain actions in-game):
    For 'yes' or 'no' prompts:
        Type either 'yes'/'y' or 'no'/'n'
    In the main screen:
        Type "start/s" to begin the game
        Type "leader/l" to view the leaderboard
        Type "quit/q" to quit the game
    In game, viewing the list of puzzles:
        Type the number of the puzzle to try and solve it (e.g. 1)
        Type "quit/q" to quit the game
    While solving a puzzle:
        Type "hint/h" to view the hint for the puzzle
        Type "back/b" to return to the list of puzzles